title: 'Ultimate Comfy'
body: After 2 years of use I can say with a lot of conviction that it is one of the comfortable shoes out there. It's light, it's soft, and yet it's sturdy.  Don't use it for sports much though, not for that.

title: 'Nice & Lightweight - Good for running & walking'
body: I bought this for my father's daily evening walk. So far so, the product is genuine and up to my expectations. It's simplistic in design, very lightweight and have a decent degree of water resistance. I cannot comment on longevity as it's been a month or so. But it's certainly worth-buying considering the features and the brand promise as well.
